title: #73 - Bo Burnham
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast (experience) we are joined in studio by the world's second most successful YouTuber: Bo Burnham! Together Bo and Ethan discuss his feature film debut- Eighth Grade, as well as the state of the internet, videos from the depth of YouTube, anxiety, and a little kid named Beau. Bo Burnham is a stand-up comedian, actor, director and all around great guy. His film, Eighth Grade, is in select theaters starting July 13th!
